    response: { en: 'Water Intake Calculator — Personalized Guide: THE FORMULA: Minimum: 30-35ml per kg of bodyweight. Example: 80kg person = 2.4-2.8 liters per day MINIMUM. ADD MORE FOR: Training days: +500ml-1L (depending on sweat). Hot weather (Egypt summer!): +500ml-1L. High protein diet: +500ml (kidneys need water to process protein). Caffeine intake: +250ml per cup of coffee. PRACTICAL TARGETS: 60kg person: 2-2.5L daily. 70kg person: 2.5-3L daily. 80kg person: 2.8-3.5L daily. 90kg person: 3-4L daily. 100kg person: 3.5-4.5L daily. HOW TO KNOW IF HYDRATED: Urine color chart: Clear/light yellow = hydrated. Dark yellow = dehydrated. Note: B-vitamins turn urine bright yellow (normal, don\'t worry). TIPS: Keep water bottle with you at ALL times. Drink 500ml immediately upon waking. Set phone reminders every 2 hours. Flavor with lemon/cucumber/mint if plain water is boring. Cold water is absorbed faster. CAN YOU DRINK TOO MUCH? Yes — hyponatremia (water intoxication) is real but rare. Don\'t force more than 1L per hour. DURING TRAINING: Sip 200-300ml every 15-20 minutes. Add electrolytes for sessions over 60 minutes.', ar: 'حاسبة شرب المية: المعادلة: 30-35مل لكل كجم. مثال: 80كجم = 2.4-2.8 لتر/يوم كحد أدنى. ضيف أكتر: أيام التمرين: +500مل-1 لتر. حر (صيف مصر!): +500مل-1 لتر. بروتين عالي: +500مل. كافيين: +250مل/فنجان. أهداف عملية: 60كجم: 2-2.5 لتر. 80كجم: 2.8-3.5 لتر. 100كجم: 3.5-4.5 لتر. لون البول: فاتح/شفاف = مرطّب. غامق = محتاج مية. نصائح: خد مية معاك دايماً. 500مل أول ما تصحى. ريمايندر كل ساعتين. في التمرين: 200-300مل كل 15-20 دقيقة.' },
