    stateId: 'info_cheat_meal_science',
    response: { en: 'Cheat Meals — The Science & Psychology: ONE BAD MEAL WON\'T RUIN YOU: To gain 1 kg of fat, you need to eat ~7700 cal ABOVE your maintenance. One 3000 cal cheat meal = maybe 1500 cal surplus = 0.2 kg fat at most. The scale might jump 1-2 kg next day but that\'s WATER + FOOD WEIGHT, not fat. It comes off in 2-3 days. THE PSYCHOLOGY PROBLEM: "Cheat" implies you\'re doing something wrong. This creates guilt → restrict → binge → guilt cycle. Better approach: call it a "free meal" or "flexible meal." THE SMART APPROACH: Plan it in advance (it\'s a treat, not a loss of control). Eat slowly, enjoy it. Don\'t use it as an excuse to eat everything in sight. Resume normal eating the next meal (not "I\'ll start Monday"). Consider using it as a refeed (high carb, moderate protein). FREQUENCY: Cutting: 1 free meal per week is fine. Maintenance: 2-3 per week is fine. Bulking: You\'re already eating a lot, "cheating" means less. DAMAGE CONTROL: Train before your free meal (calories go to muscle). Keep protein high even in free meal. Don\'t drink alcohol with it (body prioritizes alcohol metabolism → fat storage increases). Don\'t starve yourself the next day to "make up for it" — just eat normally.', ar: 'التشيت ميل — العلم والنفسية: وجبة واحدة مش هتدمرك: عشان تكسب 1 كجم دهون، محتاج تاكل ~7700 سعرة فوق المينتننس. الميزان ممكن يزيد 1-2 كجم تاني يوم بس ده مية + وزن أكل، مش دهون. بيروح في 2-3 أيام. مشكلة النفسية: "غش" بيخلّيك تحس بذنب → تحرم نفسك → تاكل كتير → ذنب. أحسن: سمّيها "وجبة حرة". الطريقة الذكية: خططها مسبقاً. كُل ببطء. ما تخلّيهاش عذر تاكل كل حاجة. كمّل عادي الوجبة الجاية. التكرار: تنشيف: مرة/أسبوع. مينتننس: 2-3/أسبوع. نصائح: اتمرن قبلها. بروتين عالي حتى فيها. ما تجوّعش نفسك تاني يوم.' },
