    stateId: 'info_body_recomp_deep',
    response: { en: 'Body Recomposition — Lose Fat & Build Muscle Simultaneously: IS IT POSSIBLE? Yes, but mainly for: Beginners (first 6-12 months of training). People returning after a long break (muscle memory). Overweight beginners (lots of stored energy). People on steroids (not relevant for natural discussion). HOW IT WORKS: Eat at maintenance calories (not surplus, not deficit). High protein (2-2.5g per kg bodyweight). Strength train 3-5x per week with progressive overload. Sleep 7-9 hours. Be patient — it\'s SLOW (1-2 lbs of muscle per month, 1-2 lbs of fat loss). THE PROTOCOL: Calories: Maintenance (TDEE calculator). Protein: 2-2.5g/kg (highest priority). Training: Heavy compounds + moderate isolation. Progressive overload is non-negotiable. Rest: 7-9 hours sleep, 2-3 rest days/week. TRACKING: Scale weight may NOT change (you\'re replacing fat with muscle). Use: progress photos (monthly), measurements (waist, arms, chest), strength numbers (going up = gaining muscle), mirror (most reliable long-term). WHO SHOULD NOT RECOMP: Intermediate/advanced lifters (too slow, better to bulk/cut cycle). Very lean people (need surplus to build muscle). People with specific deadlines (competition, wedding). REALITY CHECK: Recomp works but is 2-3x slower than dedicated bulk + cut cycles.', ar: 'ريكمبوزيشن الجسم — خسارة دهون وبناء عضل: ممكن؟ أيوه، بس أساساً لـ: مبتدئين (أول 6-12 شهر). العائدين بعد انقطاع. المبتدئين البدناء. ازاي: كُل على المينتننس (مش زيادة، مش نقص). بروتين عالي (2-2.5ج/كجم). تمرين 3-5 مرات/أسبوع بتحميل تدريجي. نوم 7-9 ساعات. بطيء (0.5-1 كجم عضل/شهر). البروتوكول: سعرات: مينتننس. بروتين: 2-2.5ج/كجم. المتابعة: الميزان ممكن ما يتغيرش (بتستبدل دهون بعضل). استخدم: صور شهرية، قياسات، أرقام القوة. الحقيقة: الريكمب بيشتغل بس أبطأ 2-3 مرات من بالك + كت.' },
