    stateId: 'info_mini_cut',
    response: { en: 'Mini Cut — Rapid Fat Loss in 4-6 Weeks: WHAT IS A MINI CUT: An aggressive but SHORT cutting phase (4-6 weeks max). Larger calorie deficit than normal cut. Used to quickly shed fat accumulated during a bulk, then return to gaining. THE PROTOCOL: Deficit: 700-1000 cal below maintenance (aggressive). Protein: 2.5-3g per kg (higher than normal to preserve muscle). Training: Maintain heavy compound lifts (reduce volume 20-30% if needed). Cardio: Add 3-4 sessions per week (walking, incline treadmill). Duration: 4-6 weeks MAXIMUM (longer = muscle loss risk). EXPECTED RESULTS: 2-4 kg fat loss in 4-6 weeks. Some water weight loss too (scale might drop 3-5 kg). Minimal muscle loss if protein is high enough. WHO SHOULD MINI CUT: People mid-bulk who got too fluffy. Anyone who gained excess fat over holidays. People who want to look good for an event in 4-6 weeks. WHO SHOULD NOT: Very lean people (already under 12%). People who tend to have eating disorder patterns. Complete beginners (just train and eat normally). AFTER THE MINI CUT: Slowly increase calories back to maintenance over 1 week (reverse diet). Then return to lean bulk. Don\'t yo-yo between extreme cuts and bulks.', ar: 'ميني كت — خسارة دهون سريعة: ايه الميني كت: كت عنيف بس قصير (4-6 أسابيع بس). عجز سعرات أكبر. البروتوكول: عجز: 700-1000 سعرة تحت المينتننس. بروتين: 2.5-3ج/كجم (أعلى عشان تحافظ على العضل). تمرين: حافظ على المركبات التقيلة. كارديو: 3-4 جلسات/أسبوع. المدة: 4-6 أسابيع بحد أقصى. النتائج: 2-4 كجم دهون في 4-6 أسابيع. بعد الميني كت: زوّد السعرات ببطء للمينتننس في أسبوع. ارجع للين بالك.' },
